      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 15.1 - 老子 15.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 15.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>古之善為士者，微妙玄通，深不可識。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The skilful masters (of the Dao) in old times, with a subtle and exquisite penetration, comprehended its mysteries, and were deep (also) so as to elude men's knowledge.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-015__align-002">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-015</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
