      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 15.4 - 老子 15.5</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 15.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>夫唯不可識，故強為之容。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>As they were thus beyond men's knowledge, I will make an effort to describe of what sort they appeared to be.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-015__align-003">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
