      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">3</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 15.12 - 老子 15.13</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 15.9 - 老子 15.11</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>混兮其若濁。孰能濁以靜之徐清？</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Who can (make) the muddy water (clear)? Let it be still, and it will gradually become clear. Who can secure the condition of rest?</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-015__align-010">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
