      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 15.14 - 老子 15.15</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 15.12 - 老子 15.13</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>孰能安以久動之徐生？保此道者不欲盈，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Let movement go on, and the condition of rest will gradually arise. They who preserve this method of the Dao do not wish to be full (of themselves).</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
