      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 15.16 - 老子 15.17</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 15.14</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>夫唯不盈，故能蔽不新成。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>It is through their not being full of themselves that they can afford to seem worn and not appear new and complete.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
